Class RuleObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.th_nuernberg.bluehome.RuleProcessObjects.RuleObject

  • public class RuleObject
extends java.lang.Object
    RuleObject is used to descripe dependencies between SourceObject and ActionObject. It contains a SourceObjcect to compare Against as well as all compare cases.
